<DOCOLDNO>IA031-000656-B024-165</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.atr.org:80/cir/press/pr061796a.html 204.71.237.87 19970209063448 text/html 21826
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
