202) 933-8400

      -and-

Mitchell A. Tyner
Office of General Counsel
General Conference of
 Seventh-day Adventists
12501 Old Columbia Pike
Silver Spring, Maryland 20904
(301) 690-6322

Counsel for Plaintiff Columbia Union College
</PRE>
