<a href="edit/july4prc.htm"><b>The Conservatism of the Declaration of Independence</b></a>

<dd>
    -- By Thomas G. West
<p>
<I>America has fewer liberties, less equality, and much less democracy than it did even a generation ago. Thomas Jefferson would be appalled.</I>
<br clear=all>
<p>

<dt>

   <IMG ALIGN=left SRC  = "images/button.gif" HSPACE=5 vspace=5>

