<a href="citguide.html">A Citizen's Guide to the Affirmative Action</a><br> <i>by Douglas A. Jeffrey and Brian T. Kennedy</i><p>
<a href="fairness.html">America's Passion for Fairness</a><br> <i>by Larry P. Arnn</i><p>
<a href="trainwrk.html">The Affirmative Action Trainwreck</a><br> <i>by Edward J. Erler</i><p>
<p>
