http://www.atr.org:80/claremont/affirm/wood.htm 204.71.237.87 19970209063741 text/html 98480
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Sunday, 09-Feb-97 06:38:07 GMT
Last-modified: Saturday, 08-Feb-97 08:11:34 GMT
