<DOCHDR>
http://www.atr.org:80/mrc/mediawatch/96conve.html 204.71.237.87 19970209064620 text/html 45263
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Sunday, 09-Feb-97 06:46:57 GMT
