<p>
<font size=3>YES! I want to join the nonprofit Savers &amp; 
Investors League to fight for sound, common sense taxation of personal 
savings and investments.  Please enroll me as the newest member. I understand that my Member Information will not be disclosed to any outside group for any reason.<br> <p>
