http://www.atr.org:80/savers/member.html 204.71.237.87 19970209065556 text/html 3327
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Sunday, 09-Feb-97 06:56:43 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 02-Jan-97 20:46:14 GMT
