<HEAD>

<TITLE>Schedule and Themes of Meetings -- TRC
</TITLE>

<META NAME="GENERATOR" CONTENT="Internet Assistant for Microsoft Word 2.0z Beta">
</HEAD>

<BODY">
<img src="/taxcom/logo.gif" alt="TRC" align="left">
<P>
<br>
<CENTER>
<br><P>
<h2>Schedule and Themes of Meetings</h2>
</CENTER>
<hr>
<P><br>
<font size="-1"><a href="/taxcom/order.html">Requesting Transcripts</a></font>
<P><font size="+1"><B>June</B></font>
<UL>
 <B>June 14</B> Launch meeting in Washington; News conference to
introduce commissioners
<P>
 <B>June 28</B> <a href="/taxcom/m6-28-5.html">Hearing in Washington</a>: <I>&quot;Review of major
alternative proposals&quot;</I>
</ul>
<font size="+1"><B>July</B></font>
<ul>
 <B>July 12</B> Hearing in Washington: <I> &quot;Compliance costs
and burdens&quot;</I>
<P>
 <B>July 19</B> Hearing in Boston:  <I>&quot;The Massachusetts experience with economic growth and
tax reform&quot;</I>
<P>
 <B>July 26</B> Hearing in Washington: <I>&quot;Promises and pitfalls of comprehensive tax reform:  Views
of the American people&quot;</I>
</ul>
<font size="+1"><B>August</B></font>
<ul>
 <B>Aug. 2</B> <a href="/taxcom/trc-802.html">Hearing in Omaha, Nebraska</a> <I>&quot;The Perspective from the farm community, business and
industry&quot;</I>
<P>
 <B>Aug. 16</B> Hearing in Charlotte,  North Carolina <I>&quot;Entrepreneurship; State and local taxation; International
competitiveness&quot;</I>
<P>
<B>Aug. 22</B> Hearing in Palo Alto, California  <I>&quot;Creating new businesses and industries:  The view from
Silicon Valley&quot;</I>
</ul>

<font size="+1"><B>September</B></font>
<ul>
 <B>Sept. 6</B> Hearing in Washington, DC  <I>&quot;Views on the economics of taxation; Perspective on
real estate&quot;</I>
<P>
 <B>Sept. 8</B> Hearing in South-Central Los Angeles  <I>&quot;Impact of tax policy on minority businesses and access
to capital&quot;</I> 
<P>
<B> Sept. 20</B> Hearing in New York City  <I>&quot;From Harlem to Wall Street:  Perspectives on inner-city
entreprenuership&quot;</I>
<P>
<B>Sept. 26</B> Hearing in Washington, DC  <I>&quot;The impact of tax reform on inner-city business development&quot;</I>
<P>
 <B>Sept. 27</B> Hearing in Cleveland  <I>&quot;Historical perspectives on tax reform; Business &amp;
individual taxpayer concerns&quot;</I>
</ul>
<font size="+1"><B>October-December</B></font>
<ul>
  Commission meetings to <B>develop</B> recommendations and report
</ul>
<font size="+1"><B>January</B></font>
<ul>
   <B>Release</B> of Tax Reform Commission recommendations 
</ul>
</blockquote>
<P><P>
