http://www.atr.org:80/wash_times/stories/top.html 204.71.237.87 19970209070049 text/html 10746
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Sunday, 09-Feb-97 07:01:33 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 03-Feb-97 10:20:46 GMT
