<head>
<title>Young America's Foundation Speakers Program</title>
</head>
<body background="/yaf/ground2.gif">
<p align=center>
<img src="/yaf/speakers.gif" alt="Young America's Foundation Speakers Program">
</p>
<p>Young America's Foundation conducts the largest campus outreach program in America.  Our extensive speakers program places hundreds of nationally prominent conservative lecturers on college campuses across the United States.</p>
<p>Soon, this page will highlight some of the Foundation's most exciting campus lecturers, along with bios, pictures and excerpts from their speeches.  Foundation speakers include William F. Buckley, Oliver North, Edwin Meese, Walter Williams, Robert Novak, Dan Quayle, Bay Buchanan, Dinesh D'Souza, and Star Parker, to name just a few.</P>
<p>In the meantime, if you would like to sponsor a conservative speaker on your campus, please call <b>Pat Coyle</b> or <b>Steve Slivinski</b> at (703) 318-9608, or e-mail us at <a href="mailto:yaf@yaf.org">yaf@yaf.org.</p>
[ <a href="home.html">Home</a> ]<p><p>
</body>
