http://www.atr.org:80/yaf/jobs.html 204.71.237.87 19970209070326 text/html 4463
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Sunday, 09-Feb-97 07:04:05 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 28-Oct-96 18:49:40 GMT
Content-length: 4280
