<a name="top"></a>
<blockquote><center><h2>Triumphs & Traps: What's Ahead for Conservatives</h2>
<br><b><i>Policy Review: The Journal of American Citizenship</i><br>
<a href="/heritage/p_review/jan97/toc.html">January-February 1997, Number 81</a></b>
</center><p>

<table border=0 cellpadding=5 cellspacing=5 align=right>

<tr><td valign=top>
<font size="-1"><b><i>Contributors:</i><p>


<a href="#armey">Dick Armey</a><br>
<a href="#alex">Lamar Alexander</a><br>
<a href="#norq">Grover G. Norquist</a><br>
<a href="#faris">Jack Faris</a><br>
<a href="#bush">Jeb Bush</a><br>
<a href="#bauer">Gary Bauer</a><br>
<a href="#forb">Steve Forbes</a><br>
<a href="#brown">Sam Brownback</a><br>
<a href="#pipes">Sally C. Pipes </a><br>
<a href="#fund">John H. Fund</a><br>
<a href="#good">John C. Goodman</a><br>
<a href="#pitn">John J. Pitney Jr. </a><br>
<a href="#wood">Robert L. Woodson</a><br>
<a href="#hutch">Kay Bailey Hutchison</a><br>
<a href="#dupont">Pete du Pont</a><br>
